snippet.title: V-Tech Rampage Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Credits go to PiGPEN and his website www.googumproduce.com for making V-Tech Rampage. This is a walk-through for the game because some people are having trouble on what to do even though it's pretty easy.

Part 1 - Kill Emily and anyone who screams then go back to your dorm.

Part 2 - Avoid cops, mail package, and go to Norris Hall

Part 3 - Kill everyone.
